    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>梦境与脑神经科学！动作RPG《迷途梦境》即将登场！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白天教书育人，黑夜探索梦境，感受化学老师&amp;炼金术师“小楠”的双面人生！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超人气心理学家弗洛伊德的精神分析理论，让校园养成与3d箱庭银河城有机结合！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日有所思夜有所梦，白天在现实世界的各种行为，将对夜晚的梦境产生重大影响！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开谜团，认识自己，拯救世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >教师模拟器？新手教师在白天勇闯校园！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中的白天，扮演新手化学老师渡过完整的一天，体验独属于中国式教师的辛劳、成长与喜悦！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/72e4c0b9f2c747e86acfc9aa7f7a2fd6.poster.avif?t=1763857989\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/72e4c0b9f2c747e86acfc9aa7f7a2fd6.webm?t=1763857989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/72e4c0b9f2c747e86acfc9aa7f7a2fd6.mp4?t=1763857989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >箱庭银河城！炼金术师在夜晚大杀四方！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中的夜晚，化身炼金术师体验街机光枪般的爽快射击，并结合闪避、弹反、处决、暗杀等动作探索一个个风格迥异的梦境！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/5f2776c19fe8152e9c353773376bb449.poster.avif?t=1763857989\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/5f2776c19fe8152e9c353773376bb449.webm?t=1763857989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/5f2776c19fe8152e9c353773376bb449.mp4?t=1763857989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >养成独居少女？装点自己的公寓吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中的傍晚，开启属于自己的独居生活！在商城购买家具、生活用具、玩具甚至是电子游戏！家里越温馨，梦境中就越强！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/38943a5c955a4657f0a557b3001ea790.poster.avif?t=1763857989\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/38943a5c955a4657f0a557b3001ea790.webm?t=1763857989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/38943a5c955a4657f0a557b3001ea790.mp4?t=1763857989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备你的梦境！日有所思夜有所梦！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >入梦前的各种活动将产生对应的“神经记忆”！白天做出的种种行为将深度影响晚上的梦境环境和角色的RPG强度！积极为梦境做准备吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/24973afe29a7f36500bc3ad3448886d5.poster.avif?t=1763857989\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/24973afe29a7f36500bc3ad3448886d5.webm?t=1763857989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110510/extras/24973afe29a7f36500bc3ad3448886d5.mp4?t=1763857989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
